<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/freelance/9way.css" />
  <title><%= process.env.TITLE %></title>

  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script>
    var socket = io.connect('/');

    function getNew9Way() {
      socket.emit('getNew9Way');
    }

    socket.on('9WayBoard', function(string) {
      document.getElementById('dynamic_9way').innerHTML = string;
    });

  </script>
</head>

<body onload="getNew9Way()">

  <% include ../partials/pre-nav.ejs %>
  <% include ../partials/post-nav.ejs %>

  <div class='highlight-page-section'>
    <div class='content'>

      <div class='column-container page-height'>
        <div class='column'>
          <h1 style='margin:0;padding-top:10px;'>Matt Bertoncello</h1>
          <img class='mb-portrait' src='/images/portrait.png'>
          <p class='marketing'>
            Hello and thank you for arriving at my personal website. <a href='/projects'>Here</a>, you will find a collection of projects in various stages of completion.
          </p>
          <p class='marketing'>
            To learn more about me, please browse my <a href='/about'>About</a> page.
          </p>
          <p class='marketing'>
            Kind regards,</br>Matt Bertoncello.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='column sec-fill title-page-register'>
          <div class='title-page-card'>
            <h1>Notable Projects</h1>
            <a class='title-project-link title-project-link-notify' href='#notify'>
              <span class='title-project-link-text'>Notify</span>
            </a>
            <a class='title-project-link title-project-link-ultimate' href='#ultimate'>
              <span class='title-project-link-text'>Ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe</span>
            </a>
            <a class='title-project-link title-project-link-messenger' href='#messenger'>
              <span class='title-project-link-text'>Messanger Service</span>
            </a>
            <a class='title-project-link title-project-link-website' href='#thiswebsite'>
              <span class='title-project-link-text'>This Website</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='page-section-notify-title'>
    <div class='anchor' id='notify'></div>
    <div class='content'>
      <div class='column-container page-height'>
        <div class='column'>
          <img class='notify-title' src='/images/notify-title.svg'>
          <p class='marketing'>
            Notify provides developers and organisations with secure endpoints to send customisable notifications
            to the companion mobile application. This means you no longer have to create your own application to have
            complete control over your notification content, aethetics and tracking. See <a href='/freelance/notify'>here</a>
            for more information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='page-section-ultimate-title'>
    <div class='anchor' id='ultimate'></div>
    <div class='content'>
      <div class='column-container page-height'>
        <div class='column'>
          <div class='card-ultimate-title'>
            <div class="card-header" id="dynamic_9way" onclick="getNew9Way()" alt="Click to look at more games"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='column'>
          <h1 class='card-ultimate-title bold'>Ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe</h1>
          <div class='card-ultimate-title'>
            <p class='marketing'>
              Ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe consists of 9 separate tic-tac-toe boards. Each turn, a player can play in one of the
              smaller tic-tac-toe boards. This smaller board is determined based on the previous player's selection. For this reason,
              it is a much more strategic game than the original.
            </p>
            <p class='marketing'>
              Eventually, an AI will be trained to play this game against humans. Proposed solutions are minimax variants or monte-carlo simulations.
            </p>
            <p class='marketing'>
              Play Ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe <a href='/freelance/9way'>here</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='page-section-messenger-title'>
    <div class='anchor' id='messenger'></div>
    <div class='content'>
      <div class='column-container page-height'>
        <div class='column hide-mobile-nav title-img-hermes'>
          <img src='/images/hermes/hermes-white.png'>
        </div>
        <div class='column'>
          <h1 class='bold'>Messenger Service</h1>
          <p class='marketing'>
            This instant messenging service, dubbed 'Hermes', uses sockets to communicate real-time with the NodeJS server
            and any other clients participating in the chat. Currently, messages are stored in plain-text in the MongoDB
            database - but the goal is to learn and implement end-to-end encryption.
          </p>
          <p class='marketing'>
            Find out more about <a href='/freelance/hermes' style='font-weight:800;'>Hermes</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='column hide-mobile-nav title-img-hermes flip-x'>
          <img src='/images/hermes/hermes-white.png'>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='page-section-thiswebsite-title'>
    <div class='anchor' id='thiswebsite'></div>
    <div class='content'>
      <div class='column-container page-height'>
        <div class='column title-thiswebsite-img'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/heroku.png'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/express.jpeg'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/ejs.jpg'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/nodejs.png'>
        </div>
        <div class='column'>
          <h1 class='bold'>This Website</h1>
          <p class='marketing'>
            This website is hosted by <a href='https://heroku.com'>Heroku</a>. It is running off a NodeJS
            server connected to a MongoDB databse hosted by <a href='https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas'>Atlas</a>.
            The NodeJS server renders Embedded JavaScript Templates and maintains a socket connection for specific
            pages to enable real-time client-server communication.
          </p>
          <p class='marketing'>
            I am using this website as a platform to develop hobby projects and gain experience in areas of software
            development that cannot be taught.
          </p>
          <p class='marketing'>
            Read more about this website <a href='/freelance/this-website'>here</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='column title-thiswebsite-img'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/github.png'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/mongodb-atlas.png'>
          <img src='/images/this-website/socket.png'>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
